feat(broker): add additive capabilities field to agent registration

Adds optional `capabilities` list to agent_info dict in register_agent().
Capabilities are passed via the existing `metadata` dict — no signature
change. Defaults to [] when absent, preserving full backward compatibility.

Enables programmatic capability discovery via GET /agents. Required by
coordination layer Enhancement C and Day 4 multi-agent orchestration.

Verification: existing 17 protocol tests pass + manual curl verification.
